Verify api key

->create api proxy -> pre flow -> request -> add verify api key policy

-> create api products -> create new api and save it 

-> app -> add api product to app

-> postman -> url/proxy?apikey= same as app key value

<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="yes"?>
<VerifyAPIKey continueOnError="false" enabled="true" name="Verify-API-Key-1">
    <DisplayName>Verify API Key-1</DisplayName>
    <Properties/>
    <APIKey ref="request.queryparam.apikey"/>
</VerifyAPIKey>
